# Test before deploy

**Ship tests with the change.** New or changed behavior must have unit/feature tests in the same PR/commit. **Never deploy until the matching suite is green locally.**

## Portfolio frontend (`src/`)

Any edit to React components, routing, admin shell, CMS consumers, or portfolio logic:

```bash
CI=true npm test -- --watchAll=false --passWithNoTests
```

Add or extend tests under `src/**/*.test.js` (e.g. `src/pages/Index.test.js`, `src/v3/admin/*.test.js`). Release/deploy also requires `CI=true npm run build` — see skill **deploy-portfolio**.

## Hosting outreach (`api-carlxaeron/hosting-php/`)

Any edit to `src/outreach.php`, mail helpers, cron scripts, or cadence/max-follow-up logic:

```bash
php api-carlxaeron/hosting-php/tests/run-unit.php
```

Must exit **0**. Only then `hosting_upload` / sync to Stellar.

Sequence under test: **3d → 7d → 7d → 7d**, max **4** follow-ups (`cadence: 3d1w`).

## Laravel API (`api-carlxaeron/`)

```bash
cd api-carlxaeron && php artisan test
```

Required before deploying Laravel app files to `public_html/api-carlxaeron/`. Add Feature/Unit tests for new admin routes, CMS sections, and API contracts.

## Firebase Cloud Functions (`functions/`)

```bash
cd functions && npm test
```

If no test script exists yet, run at least a syntax/load check (`node -c` / require smoke) and say so — then add tests when touching non-trivial logic. Prefer `npm test` once defined.

Required before `firebase deploy --only functions` / `npm run deploy`.

## Agent checklist

```
Change + deploy gate:
- [ ] New/changed behavior has tests in the same change set
- [ ] Identify which surface changed (src / hosting-php / Laravel / functions)
- [ ] Run the matching unit/feature tests — all green
- [ ] Only then deploy (push main / hosting-ssh upload / Firebase)
- [ ] Smoke: carlmanuel.com (portfolio) or curl https://api.carlmanuel.com/health (API)
```

## Do not

- Ship behavior without tests “to save time” — add focused tests with the change
- Deploy broken cadence/maxFollowUps changes without updating `tests/run-unit.php` expectations
- Skip outreach unit tests “just for a small fix” on `outreach.php`
- Ship hosting cron script changes without re-running unit tests
- Release portfolio v3 without `CI=true npm test` green
